org.pvg.plasmagraph.utils.data

Class DataSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pvg.plasmagraph.utils.data.DataSet

  • public class DataSet
extends java.lang.Object

    Container of the data in a graph before conversion into a JFreeChart Dataset type.

    Provides methods to create JFree Datasets.

    Author:
    Plasma Visualization Group

      • getColumnArray

        public double[] getColumnArray(int i)

        Makes a copy of one of the two columns as a doubles array based on the index provided.

        Parameters:
        i - The column to select. 0 signals the X column, whereas 1 signals the Y column. Any other value is invalid.
        Returns:
        An array of doubles containing a copy of the current state of the X or Y Column, or an array with one "0.0" value if the index is invalid.
